summary:
With my strong track record of delivering high-quality work and passion for making a positive impact, I excel in diverse and challenging environments. I am a collaborative communicator and relationship builder, known for my attention to detail and commitment to continuous learning. 

Currently, I am working as a Conference Project Manager at Management Events, I thrive in fast-paced environments and excel at coordinating successful conferences. Feel free to reach out if you are interested in speaking opportunities at one of our physical events or wish to discuss collaborations!

* Defining target groups, conducting business research, and identifying upcoming trends and challenges

- Create marketing materials and briefing
